column5: Just wanted to let a bunch of you know that fellow Fish-A-Thon'r/WFN Ambassador/Good Guy, Daniel Roy will be on CBC tomorrow morning at 6:12am for a live interview to promote Port Rowan in the Ultimate Fishing Town contest. And if you could vote for Port Rowan  http://www.wfn.tv/ultimate-fishing-town/Port-Rowan
I'm on the list and voting twice a day bro!
Just want to put in a plug for Sioux Narrows- Nestor Falls on beautiful Lake of the Woods.
